Peru Is on ‘Steady Path’ for Rating Increase, Moody’s Says

-- B y   B e n   B a i n
-- 
2011-03-03T18:43:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-03/peru-is-on-steady-path-for-rating-increase-moody-s-says.html
  Peru  is on a “steady path” to
receiving credit-rating increases, said Patrick Esteruelas, an
analyst at Moody’s Investors Service.  Moody’s may raise Peru’s rating in the next year or two,
Esteruelas said at an event in  New York .  To contact the reporter on this story:
